<!--
Note on adding new Units: you can find a template mod for adding a new Unit in the game's DoorKickers2/mods/ subfolder
-->
<Units>
	<!--
		'name' uniquely identifies this unit throughout the xml files
		'nameUI' is the localized version that shows up in the game's UI, therefore needs not be unique and is not referenced anywhere in the xml files
		'supply' is how much a single trooper from that class will count in total supply allowed for a map. One slot = 100 supply
		'flagTex' will show up in various places. Needs to have an alpha channel.
		'flagColor' will color various elements of the deploy panel
		'movie' is optional, shows up in the new squad creation screen, or when unlocking this unit
		'rndNameEntry' are the variation of random names that get automatically assigned when creating a new squad of this unit. Will also work with a single name.
		'incapacitationChance' chance to become incapacitated instead of dying (campaign only)
		'incapacitationChanceCrit' chance to become incapacitated when receiving a crit instead of dying (campaign only)
	-->

</Units>
